title: Update: They're Separated And Getting Married?!
description:
She was freaking out because she and her fiancé want to cancel their wedding, but she felt guilty and didn’t want to disappoint their parents. They were thinking of going through with the wedding and divorcing after. What did they decide to do? We have an update!
